<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Organization</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0e2f52; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .email-container { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content p { color: #5a6c7d; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        .content p strong { color: #0e2f52; }
        .info-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0987c9; }
        .info-card h2 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #0e2f52; font-size: 18px; }
        .info-card p { margin: 0; }
        .steps { margin: 25px 0; }
        .step { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .step-number { width: 30px; height: 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; color: white; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .step-text { color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 4px; }
        .note { background: #e0f2fe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .note p { margin: 0; color: #0369a1; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .footer p { margin: 0; color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer .brand { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Pending Approval</h1>
            <p>Thank you for registering!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= organizationName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering your organization with Volunteens! Your account is currently pending approval.</p>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>What happens next?</h2>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div class="step-text">Our team will review your organization details</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div class="step-text">A member of our sales team may contact you for additional information</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <div class="step-text">Once approved, you'll receive an email with access to your dashboard</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="note">
                <p>The approval process typically takes 1-2 business days. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="brand">Volunteens</span> - Connecting young volunteers with opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
